<h2>Sign in to <%= @app_name %></h2>

<p>Click the button below to sign in to your account. No password needed.</p>

<a href="<%= @magic_url %>" class="btn">Sign In</a>

<hr class="divider">

<p class="muted">
  This link expires in <strong><%= distance_of_time_in_words(@expires_in) %></strong>
  and can only be used once.
</p>

<p class="muted">
  If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this URL into your browser:<br>
  <a href="<%= @magic_url %>" style="color: #666; word-break: break-all;"><%= @magic_url %></a>
</p>

<p class="muted">If you didn't request this link, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
